dct_description_sm: par J. Cvijić ; Dressée par A. Lazić ; Gravé chez L. Wuhrer, Paris _ Imp. Dufrenoy.
Relief shown by gradient tings, contours, spot heights.
Legend of symbols and color key for elevations.
Shows land routes, railroads, cities and towns, Karst border, waterways, drainage divide line between the Adriatic the Sava.
